Package aston.group17.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bike
    A Bike vehicle, child class of Vehicle
    Car
    A Car vehicle, child class of Vehicle
    Driver
    A Driver, who will join the Pump, Till and Shop and initally managed by the Station.
    DriverTest
    JUnit test case for Driver class.
    Pump
    A Pump which contains a queue of Drivers, belongs to a Station instance and allows Driver to refill their Vehicle
    PumpTest
    JUnit test case for Pump class.
    Sedan
    A Sedan vehicle, child class of Vehicle
    Shop
    A Shop which handles shopping Drivers, if they are going to shop, and sends Drivers to the Till when they are done shopping
    Station
    The Station handles the initial entrance of a Driver and contains both the Shop and Pumps.
    StationTest
    JUnit test for the Station class.
    Till
    The Till class contains a queue of Drivers and will keep track of money gained and lost
    TillTest
    JUnit test case for the Till class.
    Truck
    A Truck vehicle, child class of Vehicle
    TruckDriver
    A Driver for the Truck class, sub class of Driver.
    Vehicle
    A Vehicle belonging to a Driver, interacted with by the Driver, filling the tank of the Vehicle
    VehicleTest
    JUnit test case for Vehciles, tests filling the tank, checking the tankSize and the filled amount
